There is no need here to use another generator in your list. You can calculate the [**`length :: Foldable f =&gt; f a -&gt; Int`**](https://hackage.haskell.org/package/base-4.12.0.0/docs/Prelude.html#v:length) of the group `xs` here. We use here an [*as-pattern* [zvon.org]](http://zvon.org/other/haskell/Outputsyntax/As-patterns_reference.html) to have both access to the entire group, and the first item of that group:

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;compress :: Eq a =&amp;gt; [a] -&amp;gt; [(a, Int)]
compress n = [ (x, &lt;b&gt;length xs&lt;/b&gt;) | &lt;b&gt;xs@&lt;/b&gt;(x:_) &amp;lt;- group n ]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

