It seems the problem lies in your &quot;ul&quot; width being too small and you&#39;re using justify-content on &quot;ul&quot; instead of &quot;li&quot;. Use this instead:
```
    ul {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
    }

    li {
        flex: 1;
        justify-content: space-around;
    }
```

